	__pthread_spin_trylock): Use constraint "m" instead of "0" for
	futex.
	* sysdeps/ia64/pt-machine.h (__compare_and_swap,
	__compare_and_swap_with_release_semantic, testandset): Use
	constraint "m" instead of "0" for futex.

