2001-04-16  Ulrich Drepper  <drepper@redhat.com>

	* signals.c (sigwait): NSIG is no signal number.  Block all
	signals while in signal handler for signals in SET.
	Patch by Manfred Spraul <manfred@colorfullife.com>.

