	* tst-cancel.c: Disable most tests.  Add new test where all
	cleanup handlers must run.
	* Makefile (tests): Add tst-cancel again.

	* cancel.c (__pthread_perform_cleanup): Correct condition for
	leaving cleanup loop early.

