	all the files which use CURRENT_STACK_FRAME.
	* sysdeps/i386/pt-machine.h (CURRENT_STACK_FRAME): Define using
	__builtin_frame_address.
	* sysdeps/i386/i686/pt-machine.h: Likewise.

