	LT_SPINLOCK_INIT, not zero.
	* spinlock.c (__pthread_unlock): Likewise.
	(__pthread_alt_lock): Likewise.
	(__pthread_alt_timedlock): Likewise.
	(__pthread_alt_unlock): Likewise.
